Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店名和我的名字一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是觉得很害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次的和风茶店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有房东小姐的话就办不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但协助我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至提供服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.57,0:07:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在是感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能帮上大家的忙是我的荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.85,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衣服送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.82,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给 妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变得很正式的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 花菱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要发呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须要在今天干完的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿和服的话不能穿内衣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.89,0:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿着内衣也可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子小姐的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在胸前垫上布比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子的胸部这么大可真不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵小姐 茶室已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是很好嘛 不是很好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.68,0:09:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像还要花很长时间嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.46,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么现在开始学习茶道的基本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并不是很难的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不用那么紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并不是紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是脚麻掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不喜欢塌塌米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脚…脚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜学长 看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长坐得很有样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么能这么没事似的正坐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先我来做个示范
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之先做到这一步看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要在今晚学会这些的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.81,0:10:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已经下定决心不再穿和服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背后的伤疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.58,0:11:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我没有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.45,0:11:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让薰少爷回想起了不愉快的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系的 我根本就没有放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.19,0:11:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧 回去吧 在这里的话会着凉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.56,0:11:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷的悲伤和痛苦由葵来承受就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.85,0:12:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 葵是薰少爷的未婚妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.09,0:12:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和薰少爷一起来承受薰少爷的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.99,0:12:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以请不要一个人独自悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来茶是这么好喝的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能再来一杯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.20,0:12:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 请稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看啊 看啊 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在看呢 在看呢 副部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然我的想法是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次绝对能盈利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样摄影部第一次的海外集训就铁定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像摄影部的店里有非常可爱的女孩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来客人来得比想像的还要多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏？怎么会到这里来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子姐姐给了我这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.95,0:13:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢 千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.56,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 好不容易来玩一趟却要你帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用挂心 不用挂心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茶已经没了 快再拿些来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 茶碗不够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,备用的茶点在哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 这就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东小姐 房东小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东小姐 这里已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都从早上一直忙到现在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜她们也已经挺熟练了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.63,0:14:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 那么我就不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店里怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 大家都很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.55,0:14:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也亏了薰少爷的宣传很成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（美味的章鱼烧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 要不要吃章鱼烧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也差不多到吃午饭的时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 好像很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很烫的 小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个 薰少爷 给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 找到了 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东小姐 妙子又把茶店弄翻天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 请马上回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易两个人单独在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心点呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 浩君 没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我送外卖去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫外卖的是走廊尽头右边的教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了 休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 那我就在这附近走走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏啊 一起去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.21,0:16:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷还要和繭一起谱写秋季故事的完结篇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么 你的休息时间还没到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.79,0:16:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 来 要洗的东西都积成堆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干什么呀 放开我…真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥 这边 这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不用这样拉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.90,0:16:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的肚子已经饿扁了 想去吃点东西
