Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.42,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是明立文化节执行委员会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的话能不能来参加这个活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请一定来
